<p><cs><col><b>Smoking bean</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <cd>the long
pod of the catalpa, or Indian-bean tree, often smoked by boys as a
substitute for cigars.</cd> -- <col><b>Smoking car</b></col>, <cd>a
railway car carriage reserved for the use of passengers who smoke
tobacco.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>smoking gun</ent>⟦br⟧
